{
  "key_path": "ImportSectionDisabled",
  "content": "To import {{importSectionName}}, enable the \"<1>{{sectionName}}</1>\" option first.",
  "content_en_sha1_hash": "9cf64c81a3605c47b7fa8b7435511c7580e9e790",
  "created_at": "2025-11-13T07:57:56.936Z",
  "updated_at": "2026-05-15T14:00:06.785Z",
  "comment": {
    "text": "This is a tooltip message that appears when an import option is disabled. It instructs the user to enable a prerequisite option before they can import the specified section. `{{importSectionName}}` is the name of the section to be imported (e.g., \"shared files and folders\"), and `<1>{{sectionName}}</1>` is the name of the option that needs to be enabled.",
    "is_auto": true,
    "updated_at": "2026-04-11T21:23:51.188Z",
    "model": "google/gemini-2.5-flash"
  },
  "usage": [
    {
      "file_path": "/packages/client/src/pages/PortalSettings/categories/data-import/components/ImportStep.tsx",
      "line_number": 246,
      "context": "}}\n isDisabled={!importOptions.importPersonalFiles}\n getTooltipContent={() => (\n <Trans\n t={t}\n i18nKey=\"ImportSectionDisabled\"\n ns=\"Settings\"\n values={{\n importSectionName: t(\n \"Settings:SharedFilesAndFolders\",\n ).toLocaleLowerCase(),",
      "module": "/packages/client"
    }
  ],
